snippet.title: Lil Gator Game is coming to PlayStation & Xbox!
snippet.description:
Save the date! Your wholesome adventure with Lil Gator and pals is coming to PlayStation 4 & 5, Xbox One & Xbox Series X|S on 10th October 2023! 

WISHLIST today! 
PlayStation: https://bit.ly/LilGatorPS
Xbox: https://bit.ly/LilGatorXbox 

Follow Playtonic Friends and MegaWobble on their socials to be kept up-to-date with more news: 
Playtonic Friends
Twitter (X): https://twitter.com/PTonicFriends
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playtonic
